SKILLS

  • Frontend: HTML, CSS, basic JavaScript, flatpickr, Framer Motion
  • Backend/Integration: WordPress, AJAX, REST API
  • CRM & Automation: HubSpot CRM, custom workflows, Stripe API
  • Analytics: GA4, Tag Manager, Clarity
  • AI: ChatGPT, prompt engineering
  • In Progress: Twilio (chat/voice bot automation), reCAPTCHA

ADDITIONAL SKILLS

  • California driver's license
  • Own personal vehicle

LANGUAGES

  • Russian (native)
  • English (intermediate)

SUMMARY

Over the past two years in the U.S., I developed and launched voyage-co.com, a booking and rental platform, along with a dedicated landing page (voyage-co.com/landing-prepurchase-lite). I managed the full product cycle — from UX/UI design and custom multi-step booking flow to CRM (HubSpot) and Stripe payment integrations, analytics (GA4, Tag Manager), and SEO. These projects reflect a hands-on full-stack approach — covering frontend UI, backend logic, CRM workflows, and performance tracking — and demonstrate my ability to deliver complete, live digital products with real user adoption. I'm now looking to apply this practical experience to larger-scale projects, deepen my expertise in AI-driven automation, and contribute to innovative product teams building scalable web solutions.

EXPERIENCE

Voyage Co – Founder / Operations & Automation Lead

Millbrae, CA • 2023 – Present

  • Designed and implemented a multi-step online booking flow (6-step), including client data collection, multi-level validation, and dynamic confirmation.
  • Developed HubSpot CRM integration, enabling automatic transfer of client information, deals, and custom parameters (address, inspection date and time) directly from booking forms.
  • Configured Stripe Payment API (PaymentIntent) for secure online payment processing, covering both server-side and client-side implementation.
  • Established a complete digital analytics system with GA4, Google Tag Manager, and Microsoft Clarity to build an end-to-end booking funnel, analyze user behavior, and optimize conversions.
  • Currently implementing Twilio-based automation: developing custom workflows and a chat/voice bot to handle client requests directly from the website, including automated confirmations and CRM updates.
  • Applied AI tools to streamline processes: content generation, scenario testing, data validation, and preparation of client communication templates.
  • Executed SEO optimization and content strategy, focusing on target keywords (“pre-purchase inspection San Francisco,” “used car inspection”), which improved visibility and increased organic traffic.

Turo Carsharing Host

2023 – Present, Bay Area, CA

  • Manage car rental operations as an independent host on Turo platform.
  • Achieved 5★ reviews and built a strong base of repeat customers.
  • Hands-on experience with digital rental platform operations, client communication, and service management.
  • Proof of successful U.S.-based entrepreneurial activity with verified customer satisfaction.

Previous International Experience (Russia, 2005–2023)

  • 15+ years in sales, business operations, and management.
  • Founded and scaled 2 businesses (auto repair center & financial brokerage).
  • 10+ years of leadership experience in banking and automotive industries.
  • Specialized in sales strategy, client operations, and team management.

EDUCATION

  • North Caucasus Social University, Stavropol, Russia
    Bachelor’s degree in Economics • 2004–2007
  • Stavropol College of Computer Engineering and Electronics
    Bank Specialist, Economist • 2001–2004

KEY ACHIEVEMENTS

  • Created and launched Voyage Co (voyage-co.com) — a fully functional booking & rental platform in the U.S., developed from the ground up.
  • Delivered a dedicated landing page (voyage-co.com/landing-prepurchase-lite) to expand services and improve lead conversion.
  • Implemented a complete digital ecosystem: HubSpot CRM, Stripe Payment API, GA4, Tag Manager, Microsoft Clarity, and SEO optimization.
  • Developed custom booking UX with multi-step forms, advanced validation, and modern interactive design.
  • Founded and scaled two auto repair centers and a financial services startup in Russia, demonstrating ability to build and grow businesses from scratch.
